    "description": "<p>MediaPlus Digital is a marketing agency, specializing in web design & development, online marketing as well as creative copy writing services. Our diverse range of clients range from small to medium enterprises who seek to expand their business by increasing their online presence. As part of the company’s growth plan, we are looking for independent, enthusiastic, creative, fun and passionate personnel to join our team as Graphic Designer with basic knowledge of online marketing. You may visit our website www.mediaplus.com.sg for more information about us.</p>\r\n",
